kind in the market right now.

333
00:16:35,954 --> 00:16:38,540
We're doing it out of passion
and of course,

334
00:16:38,665 --> 00:16:40,750
financial viability.

335
00:16:41,292 --> 00:16:43,211
So, any questions?

336
00:16:43,795 --> 00:16:46,965
Arvind, can I add a few points?

337
00:16:47,048 --> 00:16:49,050
-Yes, sure.
-Sure?

338
00:16:53,722 --> 00:16:56,307
Hi, everyone. I'm Suchitra Iyer.

339
00:16:56,433 --> 00:16:59,436
And I'd just like to add a few
points to what Nikhil said.

340
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:01,730
Normally, when others have
a small problem

341
