as we give to physical health.

352
00:17:30,133 --> 00:17:34,387
If our body has a problem,
we look for solutions.

353
00:17:34,512 --> 00:17:37,098
But if anybody
needs mental help

354
00:17:37,182 --> 00:17:38,475
which I strongly believe

355
00:17:38,558 --> 00:17:40,602
that we all do at
some point of time.

356
00:17:41,060 --> 00:17:43,229
Then, we don't know what to do.

357
00:17:43,313 --> 00:17:44,981
And we won't do anything

358
00:17:45,106 --> 00:17:48,359
