359
00:17:49,402 --> 00:17:51,863
This is where we
would like to come in.

360
00:17:51,946 --> 00:17:56,451
We want to make sure that we not
only have easy access to help.

361
00:17:56,743 --> 00:18:00,038
But we have to fight this
taboo of seeking help.

362
